Metadata.Title: Headcase
Metadata.Description: [Complication]: Once used for a kill, axes can not be picked up again.[Complication]: Any guard disguise can only be used once and for 30 seconds only.Surely there must be a logical endpoint? There's no way that man can breach the rules of nature. Targets have always gone up to five. That's the way it's always been...I'm not the crazy one here, you are.Created by : Linux Penguin (XBOX) a member of the hitmanforum.
